OL,3,C'Welcome to hell': Dangerous cladding
OL,4,Chas left families trapped or homeless
OL,6,FITV News' Social Affairs Correspondent
OL,7,FSarah Corker speaks with families
OL,8,Faffected by living in homes with
OL,9,Fflammable cladding.
OL,11,FThousands of people have been left
OL,12,Fhomeless or stuck in unsafe buildings,
OL,13,Fwith some facing financial ruin, after
OL,14,Fserious cladding defects on buildings
OL,15,Facross the country were exposed
OL,16,Ffollowing the Grenfell Tower tragedy
OL,17,Fseven years ago.
