OL,3,C'Welcome to hell': Dangerous cladding
OL,4,Chas left families trapped or homeless
OL,6,FFamilies in these defective buildings
OL,7,Fhave told ITV News they are living in
OL,8,Fmisery with devastating consequences
OL,9,Fto their mental and physical health.
OL,11,FThe social housing tenants left
OL,12,Ffreezing every winter
OL,14,FEddie Farrell's tower block in Salford
OL,15,Fwas stripped of its flammable cladding
OL,16,Fshortly after Grenfell but more than
OL,17,Ffour years later it has not been
OL,18,Freplaced and his home has been left
OL,19,Fwith no insulation.
