OL,3,C'Welcome to hell': Dangerous cladding
OL,4,Chas left families trapped or homeless
OL,6,FEvery winter hundreds of social
OL,7,Fhousing tenants are left freezing.
OL,9,FMalus Court is one of eight blocks of
OL,10,Fflats, which are owned by Salford
OL,11,Fcouncil but managed by Pendleton
OL,12,FTogether, and have been plagued with
OL,13,Fproblems for years.
OL,15,F"Welcome to Hell. It's like a building
OL,16,Fsite, dark, damp, miserable, cold. We
OL,17,Fjust feel abandoned", Mr Farrell said.
