OL,3,C'Welcome to hell': Dangerous cladding
OL,4,Chas left families trapped or homeless
OL,6,FThe building is surrounded by
OL,7,Fscaffolding and on almost every floor
OL,8,Fof Malus Court's seven storeys,
OL,9,Fwiring, lights and even smoke alarms
OL,10,Fwere hanging down precariously from
OL,11,Fthe ceiling.
OL,13,F"I don't feel safe, this exposed
OL,14,Fwiring has been like this for a year"
OL,15,FMr Farrell said as he points to the
OL,16,Fceiling. "It's like living in a slum."
OL,18,FThe situation has taken a toll on the
OL,19,F62-year-old's health.
