OL,3,C'Welcome to hell': Dangerous cladding
OL,4,Chas left families trapped or homeless
OL,6,F"I've had three heart attacks since I
OL,7,Fhave been in this block," Mr Farrell
OL,8,Fsaid. "It's stress. Sometimes it can
OL,9,Fget so cold here you can see you
OL,10,Fbreath in the living room."
OL,12,FThen there's the financial strain. For
OL,13,Ffour years tenants have been paying
OL,14,Fincreased heating costs because
OL,15,Fthere's no external cladding to retain
OL,16,Fthe heat.
