OL,3,C'Welcome to hell': Dangerous cladding
OL,4,Chas left families trapped or homeless
OL,6,FMr Farrell said: "It costs me #340 a
OL,7,Fmonth to heat this place. I can't
OL,8,Fafford that, I've had to borrow money
OL,9,Foff my son. Most of the time I keep
OL,10,Fthe heating off."
OL,12,F"Seven years since Grenfell, nothing
OL,13,Fhas changed. We feel like we've just
OL,14,Fbeen dumped."
OL,16,FThe housing association has apologised
OL,17,Ffor delays to the work here and told
OL,18,Fus safety across the eight blocks is
OL,19,Fassessed on a daily basis.
