OL,6,FTenants have been given #50 pounds a
OL,7,Fmonth during the winter to help pay
OL,8,Ffor heating.
OL,10,FMichelle Allott, Executive Director
OL,11,Ffor Operations at Together Housing
OL,12,FGroup said: "While I fully accept that
OL,13,Ffor many of our residents this taking
OL,14,Ftoo long, we are working to ensure we
OL,15,Fget this right for their long term
OL,16,Fsafety and the work is unavoidable."
