OL,6,F"It's heart breaking. You see your
OL,7,Fhome and you can't step foot inside. I
OL,8,Fam still having to pay even though I
OL,9,Fcan't live here," Ms Malik told ITV
OL,10,FNews.
OL,12,FThe fire safety faults at her building
OL,13,Fin Oldham are so serious, Fozia and
OL,14,Fher neighbours were told they had to
OL,15,Fleave immediately as the fire service
OL,16,Fevacuated the whole block in 2020.
