OL,3,C'Welcome to hell': Dangerous cladding
OL,4,Chas left families trapped or homeless
OL,6,FThe 47-year-old works two jobs, seven
OL,7,Fdays a week to pay the bills for the
OL,8,FOldham flat and the rent for her
OL,9,Fhostel room.
OL,11,F"We are all suffering mentally,
OL,12,Fphysically and financially. Who is
OL,13,Fgoing to be responsible? At one point
OL,14,FI wanted to take my own life. It's my
OL,15,Fhome and no-one has the right to take
OL,16,Fmy roof from me," she said.
