OL,6,FResidential Management Group (RMG)
OL,7,Fwhich manages the building described
OL,8,Fit as a 'very complex case,' blaming
OL,9,Fthe delays on new legislation designed
OL,10,Fto protect leaseholders from the costs
OL,11,Fof remediation work.
OL,13,F"...The Building Safety Act has since
OL,14,Fbeen introduced which has made the
OL,15,Ffunding of these works more complex
OL,16,Fand has impacted progress but we have
OL,17,Fbeen working through this with the
OL,18,Flandlord," RMG said in a statement.
