OL,3,C'Welcome to hell': Dangerous cladding
OL,4,Chas left families trapped or homeless
OL,6,F"We are held back by long delays in
OL,7,Fgovernment funding," says Greater
OL,8,FManchester Deputy Mayor Kate Green.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Deputy Mayor Kate
OL,11,FGreen, who is part of the area's High
OL,12,FRise Taskforce set up in the wake of
OL,13,FGrenfell, blamed both the government
OL,14,Fand developers for the delays in
OL,15,Fmaking buildings safe.
OL,17,F"We are ultimately held back by long
OL,18,Fdelays in the government's funding
OL,19,Fregimes, and a further problem is the
OL,20,Fcapacity of the construction industry
OL,21,Fto come and carry out this work.
