OL,6,F"Some of the funding costs will be
OL,7,Fpassed to developers, which is right,
OL,8,Fbut where developers continue to drag
OL,9,Ftheir feet, people continue to be in
OL,10,Fthese terrible living circumstances,"
OL,11,Fshe told ITV News.
OL,13,FThe government is talking tough,
OL,14,Fwarning building owners to fix this
OL,15,Fcrisis or we'll take enforcement
OL,16,Faction against you.
OL,18,FRushanara Ali MP, Minister for
OL,19,FBuilding Safety, admitted the
OL,20,F"progress on remediation has been far
OL,21,Ftoo slow."
